id: pmc-api6
title: Adopt pm field-aware merge driver for multi-agent branch-merge safety
description: "Add the pm-cli 2026.7.20+ field-aware git merge driver (.gitattributes fence mapping tracker artifacts to pm-item-toon/pm-item-markdown/pm-history/pm-relationship/pm-json). Bumps @unbrained/pm-cli devDep floor to ^2026.7.21 (driver requires 2026.7.20+). Enables conflict-free field-level merges of concurrent-branch tracker edits, append-only union of history+relationship jsonl, key-level JSON config merge. Companion epic pm-cli-website-juz0."
type: Chore
status: in_progress
priority: 3
tags[3]: 2026.7.21,merge-driver,multi-agent-merge
created_at: "2026-07-21T20:46:43.449Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-21T20:46:43.449Z"
deadline: "2026-07-28T00:00:00.000Z"
assignee: claude-orchestrator
author: claude-orchestrator
estimated_minutes: 30
acceptance_criteria: "Committed .gitattributes has pm-cli:merge-drivers fence; @unbrained/pm-cli devDep floor ^2026.7.21; changelog:check passes; CI green."
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  pmc-3j77,related,"2026-07-21T20:46:43.449Z",claude-orchestrator,null
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T20:46:43.449Z",claude-orchestrator,Part of fleet-wide juz0 epic rollout; pm-github is the reference adoption (PR #5).
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T20:46:43.449Z",claude-orchestrator,git config is per-clone; each fresh clone/CI runs pm merge install once. Post-merge run pm history-repair --all (upstream auto-hook tracked as pm-cli#623).
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T20:46:43.449Z",claude-orchestrator,Field-aware driver merges divergent scalar fields AND unions array fields (notes) without conflict; history verify needs history-repair post-merge.
files[1]{path,scope,note}:
  .gitattributes,project,merge-driver fence written by pm merge install
tests[1]{command,scope,timeout_seconds}:
  git merge concurrent-branch,project,60
docs[1]{path,scope,note}:
  README.md,project,multi-agent merge safety
body: "Validated 2026-07-21 in a throwaway workspace: branch A set priority=1+noteA, branch B set assignee=agentB+noteB; git merge auto-resolved field-level (both scalar edits survived, notes[] unioned), zero conflict markers; pm validate ok:true after pm history-repair --all."
